{"tid":1957644,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[每日黄店]呦呦鹿鳴布丁燒","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T12:52:08.000Z","uid":269202,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"13899c8f754e1af0b950c05ee253fa11899edf46","tid":1957644,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZafifE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZafifE.png&h=2b83f27a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nMaCwAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnMaCwAL.png&h=cad79634&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wMqKV2x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwMqKV2x.png&h=dcde93d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50zckuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50zckuk.png&h=19d6276c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7FrpWa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7FrpWa.png&h=bab1ec15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n布丁燒聽多了，這裡有原味、咖啡和椰子味。原本想試試看若竹抹茶的甜品怎麼樣，可惜未出爐。<br />\n倒出來的體驗很好玩，側一側，布丁層就自動脫模，接著焦糖液就從蛋糕上面流向整個盤子。可能你看到那麼多焦糖液認為一定會很甜、嗆喉，實際上不是。連著芝士蛋糕層吃，是一個甜一個淡的味道。椰子味有椰肉在裡面，喜歡椰子的人可能很喜歡。要烤兩次慢烤水浴法連備料至少要2小時。$38蚊一個，這工藝在葵廣，有人會欣賞嗎？<br />\n唉！抹茶沒嚐到，又要下次再來了。<br />\n#飲食界工會 #若竹抹茶 #葵廣美食 #呦呦鹿鳴布丁燒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E5%91%A6%E5%91%A6%E9%B9%BF%E9%B3%B4%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%81%E7%87%92-1958728431103840/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E5%2591%25A6%25E5%2591%25A6%25E9%25B9%25BF%25E9%25B3%25B4%25E5%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2581%25E7%2587%2592-1958728431103840%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQyqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=6ef50fdc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E5%91%A6%E5%91%A6%E9%B9%BF%E9%B3%B4%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%81%E7%87%92-1958728431103840/</a>"},{"pid":"afb110fe1ec4a12053e44049874a1c2632cc7b81","tid":1957644,"uid":8557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"呢間野真心正<br />\n不過一個38蚊太貴唔可以成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e925048875ab608d368094ca85b8196a77f4c096","tid":1957644,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"其實店家應該推出其他時間較短的產品<br />\n<br />\n例如更小杯的芝士蛋糕<br />\n<br />\n那樣只需焗一次，價格更便宜，擴大到受眾"},{"pid":"49b713318093fa95754087b0113e4bef7086c3ff","tid":1957644,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afb110fe1ec4a12053e44049874a1c2632cc7b81","tid":1957644,"uid":8557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"呢間野真心正<br />\n不過一個38蚊太貴唔可以成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"呢幾年大概食左3 4次<br />\n太貴"},{"pid":"fcc609c5b015f24fc76801e66bff0f37b25be82b","tid":1957644,"uid":326151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:36:18.000Z","msg":"食過兩次 都係覺得頗貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"410678ba3790fe9bc08aa77ade7c09e8b7271ab9","tid":1957644,"uid":45848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T22:27:39.000Z","msg":"食過次熱baileys酒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚正，但有啲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62884ee72f804363501d2461a2b463c61cbce170","tid":1957644,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T22:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c36fe730122ade097f505104bf3eaee529848a66","tid":1957644,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T00:38:29.000Z","msg":"食過，係幾好，不過個人覺得太甜"},{"pid":"e78bdf4e833407e13eed66bdd08cb73f052333ad","tid":1957644,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T01:09:30.000Z","msg":"咁細賣38 貴過頭 大一倍就差唔多 